   \section{Conclusion}
   \subsection{Summary and Future Work}

   \section{References}

  \end{document}
   ```

2. Next, you need to use the `\tableofcontents` command to generate the table of contents. This command should be placed after the `\begin{document}` command and before the first section of your document. Here's an example:

   ```
   \tableofcontents

  \section{Introduction}
   \subsection{Background}
   \subsection{Motivation}
   \subsection{Objectives}

   \section{Related Work}
