   ```

3. Finally, you need to use the `\listoftables`, `\listoffigures`, or `\listofalgorithms` commands to generate a list of tables, figures, or algorithms in your document. These commands should be placed after the `\tableofcontents` command and before the first section of your document. Here's an example:

   ```
   \listoftables

   \tableofcontents

